{"tid":86331,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"【Binc】【抒情文】玩老鏡的我為何還未入A7?","createTime":"2017-01-19T03:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T11:56:27.000Z","uid":12709,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91d42c4858c19068247c1ff30a5cd1f253ae7e43","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之一．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，尋晚復活節慶典燭光微動，教堂裡我手持 K5IIs＋CZ Planar 50/1.4 <br />\n<br />\n無咩大作，送上2013年小品 <br />\n<a href=\"http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiplaylens.blogspot.hk%2F2013%2F03%2Fcarl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html&d=daOaZUhJ4ytZREDCrRV8yZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cee2cbc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-lV2nOcdn7e0/UVj4iF-AyGI/AAAAAAAAO5A/POzwfFTnWkI/s1600/IMGP6211.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-lV2nOcdn7e0%2FUVj4iF-AyGI%2FAAAAAAAAO5A%2FPOzwfFTnWkI%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6211.JPG&h=b9fe985d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n轉身回首一望，突然見過個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上一部A7R＋FE 35/2.8 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心中沈了一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是葡萄？是不屑？還是不解？ <br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟身邊十個玩老鏡，一半已有A7/A7R <br />\n但一個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上既應該 OMD GM1 RX100 Nikon J1 etc... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--5cysrUykpI/UVj4hJyvB4I/AAAAAAAAO40/icWR3V-nS00/s1600/IMGP6228.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F--5cysrUykpI%2FUVj4hJyvB4I%2FAAAAAAAAO40%2FicWR3V-nS00%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6228.JPG&h=0df700d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個敗家仔都問過我，點解唔入A7 解放個一百支135老鏡??? （跌到8k好似係） <br />\n<br />\n突然間想回顧下，我呢兩年半學玩攝影之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來，我一直迷失係片幅既迷思之中⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NjiAK5fY8-M/UVj4sW1iYTI/AAAAAAAAO50/klZzozPQ2qw/s1600/IMGP6248.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-NjiAK5fY8-M%2FUVj4sW1iYTI%2FAAAAAAAAO50%2FklZzozPQ2qw%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6248.JPG&h=381d80b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b529def3ad2d92476ba152744c4dade5ea6f9b1","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之二．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n玩老鏡既圈子中，FF全幅一直係磨鏡既標準裝備 <br />\n<br />\n呢幾年網上受歡迎既blogger 都係用FF香爐機身插135老鏡 <br />\ne.g. 5DII, 6D, A99, A7 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9U7dd2YCRAc/UVj4sHMlxtI/AAAAAAAAO5s/uVI6gS31bNc/s1600/IMGP6265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-9U7dd2YCRAc%2FUVj4sHMlxtI%2FAAAAAAAAO5s%2FuVI6gS31bNc%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6265.jpg&h=d2123e97&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解我仲唔入A7 解放個一百支135老鏡？ <br />\n<br />\n除左＄既問題，同埋我個人dislike貓sir既金主 <br />\n<br />\n呢個問題要去到兩年半前，我學咩係攝影開始⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tPkgFm0Jjk8/UVj4wKgyNPI/AAAAAAAAO6E/G48JgHl9mTY/s1600/IMGP6307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-tPkgFm0Jjk8%2FUVj4wKgyNPI%2FAAAAAAAAO6E%2FG48JgHl9mTY%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6307.jpg&h=dd6e6f45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－ <br />\n<br />\n以前去旅行都幾多，一年大概有兩次 <br />\n個時同家人去，多數係用部Canon A20求其影 <br />\n（之後用IXUS880、G10、350D） <br />\n用單反350D去歐洲畢業旅行，都係超新手，根本都未無心鑽研攝影 <br />\n<br />\n舊相 <a href=\"http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2012/11/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiplaylens.blogspot.hk%2F2012%2F11%2Fblog-post.html&d=daOaZUhJ4ytZREDCrRV8yZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=62089798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2012/11/blog-post.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n直至2011年尾，我用1.5k入左第一部二手APSC無反－NX100 <br />\n（呢部野好多人話 0 銷量，其實非也，有好多勇者同我一樣敢試⋯⋯有限budget<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n<br />\n當時我只係諗一樣野 <br />\nAPSC＋輕身 <br />\n<br />\n為既就係玩老豆既兩支M42定焦 <br />\nColor-Ultron 50/1.8 <br />\nHaminex 135/2.8 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--m23g-a6at8/ULMN5QhKi4I/AAAAAAAAHMY/m_J0aSI7DVU/s1600/SAM_6526.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F--m23g-a6at8%2FULMN5QhKi4I%2FAAAAAAAAHMY%2Fm_J0aSI7DVU%2Fs1600%2FSAM_6526.JPG&h=fd5e2268&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SJQP73uIuH0/ULMEG8mGITI/AAAAAAAAHGk/_oB2W22Xy6s/s1600/SAM_4515.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-SJQP73uIuH0%2FULMEG8mGITI%2FAAAAAAAAHGk%2F_oB2W22Xy6s%2Fs1600%2FSAM_4515.JPG&h=d5a9d357&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無peaking、無EVF、無CS、無人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我開始知道，咩係景深。基本攝影技巧，全部由網上自學 <br />\n<br />\n最重要既係，玩老鏡轉接－要手動對焦、測光、計flange distance <br />\n令我學野都係 由基礎學起 <br />\ne.g.點樣分SLR / RF鏡、crop factor <br />\n<br />\n幾個月後NX100半賣半送給朋友，自己就2.5k入左部99新NX11白機"},{"pid":"58dd6fc5aa968e851ffba14dda47b4e4d1b34719","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之三．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xyA-eAhZ7ZM/ULMNy1oeizI/AAAAAAAAHL4/cJ0W1GwxOj4/s1600/SAM_5593.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-xyA-eAhZ7ZM%2FULMNy1oeizI%2FAAAAAAAAHL4%2FcJ0W1GwxOj4%2Fs1600%2FSAM_5593.JPG&h=58f81921&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-g-dK_QRIMFo/ULMNr-6csKI/AAAAAAAAHLg/0Zui5hXjlUk/s1600/SAM_5381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-g-dK_QRIMFo%2FULMNr-6csKI%2FAAAAAAAAHLg%2F0Zui5hXjlUk%2Fs1600%2FSAM_5381.jpg&h=e84493eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入左***NX11後便只玩老鏡轉接 <br />\n之後，就整左個好壞參半既老鏡blog：腹黑攻XXX <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我性格一向鍾意黑馬 <br />\n人棄則我取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢慢玩老鏡數量愈來愈多，尋求NX玩到既種類 <br />\ne.g. Leica L39、Arriflex、DKL <br />\n<br />\n根據我網上search左一年 <br />\n全世界用NX玩L39、Arriflex寥寥可数 <br />\n（因為無咩人知NX 25.5mm flange distance藝能造過adapter俾28.8既L39） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gearCZQvvQo/ULy5WOveFrI/AAAAAAAAIxM/JNOC28QiGoU/s1600/EPSN1475.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-gearCZQvvQo%2FULy5WOveFrI%2FAAAAAAAAIxM%2FJNOC28QiGoU%2Fs1600%2FEPSN1475.JPG&h=90f6a9ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後大量入手L39 特別係canon <br />\n然而，因為轉接過Leica 35/3.5，眼角太低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加上***係高登有原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾高登仔 30個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－ <br />\n<br />\n大概去到2012年中 <br />\n有次轉讓老鏡時，有個大叔平讓左一個Bessa R，解放當時手頭上廿幾支L39鏡 <br />\n（只收我＄700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有心割愛） <br />\n結果就開始左初嚐FF滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋學左玩菲林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 個皮套係我熟人手製的，帶興趣自製皮套既巴打 <br />\n我可介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ec-LzCU1JH8/UpBql7mMjSI/AAAAAAAARi8/JeIgtYXZIAE/s1600/IMGP1270.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Ec-LzCU1JH8%2FUpBql7mMjSI%2FAAAAAAAARi8%2FJeIgtYXZIAE%2Fs1600%2FIMGP1270.JPG&h=4eafad22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4e6371baf71ddfaea9955128b27736e35fcdaa","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之四．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\nAPSC無反都玩了年半，心中癢癢 <br />\n是不是時候該入一部DSLR??? 特別是FF機身如5D2? <br />\n<br />\n當時A7還未有消息，只有貓sir的JJ工具－A99 <br />\n25k呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最貴既老鏡都係6k（而且一直認識老鏡保值、升值，數碼機一年打7折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n另外5D2又上了年紀（就算我家人用7D，本人對canon DSLR評價都係一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n<br />\n結果呢？ <br />\n2013農曆年，9k入了另一小眾 Pentax K5IIs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因有幾個： <br />\n1) 早入左部Bessaflex同幾部菲林機 玩M42 FF菲林 <br />\n2) 玩左大量takumar，對Pentax暗生好感 <br />\n3) Pentax DSLR有機身內置 紅點合焦提示、機身防震、接M42 adapter無厚度、無低通 <br />\n4) M42鏡有50支以上 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-XCrkkGdRXPU/Upr2yJ0J8yI/AAAAAAAARoc/Xl8fYUUngPY/s1600/IMGP1210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-XCrkkGdRXPU%2FUpr2yJ0J8yI%2FAAAAAAAARoc%2FXl8fYUUngPY%2Fs1600%2FIMGP1210.jpg&h=462cc722&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2866/11600619216_430645abbc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm3.staticflickr.com%2F2866%2F11600619216_430645abbc_b.jpg&h=3958a2b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-1Rdb7JHeZTI/UhcWHa7slJI/AAAAAAAAQZQ/iH9ufi3cu4A/s1600/IMGP9481.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-1Rdb7JHeZTI%2FUhcWHa7slJI%2FAAAAAAAAQZQ%2FiH9ufi3cu4A%2Fs1600%2FIMGP9481.JPG&h=e3f0bb20&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7qFksEVitDY/UjUYX2qEWqI/AAAAAAAAQvA/brKfjoFscXQ/s1600/IMGP9721.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-7qFksEVitDY%2FUjUYX2qEWqI%2FAAAAAAAAQvA%2FbrKfjoFscXQ%2Fs1600%2FIMGP9721.JPG&h=27d8f4b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0yPCl27-8uI/ULQo9165BcI/AAAAAAAAHX4/GGkPzlCGNog/s1600/750px-Honeywell-Pentax-Spotmatic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-0yPCl27-8uI%2FULQo9165BcI%2FAAAAAAAAHX4%2FGGkPzlCGNog%2Fs1600%2F750px-Honeywell-Pentax-Spotmatic.jpg&h=c3efec4f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後一直玩M42 <br />\nPentax 機身手感、控制，我敢話係日廠中最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n色水又鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我覺得唔差過Fujifilm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"d719442dd72ae60ca58a5d69f9a836147a70f6f6","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之五．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n大概2013年暑假後，我慢慢發現 <br />\n隨著NX11少用，L39鏡 只會放係度鋪塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時A7仲未有聲氣（就算有，我都唔係個種一出就買新機既有錢仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n我諗，我需要一部代替NX11既無反玩L39 Arriflex等RF鏡 <br />\n當時FF無反實在無咩抵用選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔鍾意NEX系列，因為手感差、JPEG色彩偏離、介面食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（而家A7用左RX100介面就好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\nM43、Nikon 1：crop factor太遠，我又少打真雀或月球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（玩老鏡散景特色cut曬為咩？） <br />\n<br />\nFujifilm其實XE1唔錯 <br />\n我上年暑假借朋友＋1855/2.8-4 去巴西影左一個月 <br />\nAstria Provia 色水真OK（當時未有peaking firmware） <br />\n返來時都打算入水XE1, 或XM1 body <br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－ <br />\n<br />\n最後又係入左超冷門 EOSM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nblue bay日水貨＋1122STM＝total 6k <br />\n<br />\n點解？7成為左支3k既ultra wide <br />\n因為老鏡本身無咩超廣角選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCV 12mm/5.6 唔用135 film 浪費曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然EOSM到而家都未有firmware加peaking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係真係平抵玩 <br />\nflange distance玩到M mount同Contax G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n22大光圈餅插來俾老豆旅行用（孝順仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n1122方便拍團體照，將來旅行兩機三鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲D學拍片又有STM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以，EOSM夠我來緊兩三年： <br />\n旅行wide、俾老豆 女友循環再用、堅持等A7跌落5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾一篇，講下幾時入FF body玩鏡既考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff515037e347d4038411d6ea87c58aa7286c4b9b","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"【感動回顧之五個半．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n正題：點解唔入A7 解放135老鏡呢??? <br />\n<br />\n小弟有以下省思 <br />\n<br />\n1) APSC片幅其實sensor都做到一定淺景深 <br />\ncrop factor未算太過份 <br />\n影小物件 其實都算方便（特別係大光圈50標頭） <br />\n<br />\n2) ultra wide鏡問題 <br />\n老鏡廣角從來都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只想玩手動，或平價under 16mm <br />\n就要問點解唔入Samyang 14mm（2.2k左右 FF可用） <br />\n<br />\n3) 高ISO <br />\nFF完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ISO1600 APSC無邊部真係OK <br />\n不過玩老鏡事實上，影夜景既機會真係少 <br />\n（上次個一路向西中環夜景post，原來好多巴打都少用老鏡影夜景） <br />\n<br />\n4) 手動輔助功能 <br />\n雖然A7或Fujifilm都有digital假裂像、peaking <br />\n但係都無Pentax 機身紅點合焦提示、機身防震，或者換真裂像屏既可能 <br />\n其實FF sensor防震得A99有??? <br />\n<br />\n5) 錢 <br />\nSony A9好似2015年初有 <br />\n到時A7二手跌至6k非impossible（而家未夠半年，由12k跌至8k） <br />\n（巴打講得啱，要認識手上既器材先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n<br />\n6) sensor技術 <br />\nFujifilm 非bayer，Sigma x3 都係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（Canon 70D double pixel唔關玩鏡事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n所以追求FF，不應只是量（面積大小） <br />\n還有質（高Dynamic Range） <br />\n<br />\n故此，我打算2015年初才考慮入FF無反 <br />\n最希望有Pentax 機身防震 FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者Fujifilm、Sigma FF <br />\n心底還希望***痴左線整部135方形sensor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc54945231dceace526516d2f7f8a5d0578c152b","tid":86331,"uid":56032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【感動回顧之一．分六篇上載】 <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，尋晚復活節慶典燭光微動，教堂裡我手持 K5IIs＋CZ Planar 50/1.4 <br />\n<br />\n無咩大作，送上2013年小品 <br />\n<a href=\"http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiplaylens.blogspot.hk%2F2013%2F03%2Fcarl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html&d=daOaZUhJ4ytZREDCrRV8yZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cee2cbc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://iplaylens.blogspot.hk/2013/03/carl-zeiss-planar-t-50mm-f14-zs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-lV2nOcdn7e0/UVj4iF-AyGI/AAAAAAAAO5A/POzwfFTnWkI/s1600/IMGP6211.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-lV2nOcdn7e0%2FUVj4iF-AyGI%2FAAAAAAAAO5A%2FPOzwfFTnWkI%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6211.JPG&h=b9fe985d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n轉身回首一望，突然見過個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上一部A7R＋FE 35/2.8 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心中沈了一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是葡萄？是不屑？還是不解？ <br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟身邊十個玩老鏡，一半已有A7/A7R <br />\n但一個廿到尾既OL <br />\n手上既應該 OMD GM1 RX100 Nikon J1 etc... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--5cysrUykpI/UVj4hJyvB4I/AAAAAAAAO40/icWR3V-nS00/s1600/IMGP6228.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F--5cysrUykpI%2FUVj4hJyvB4I%2FAAAAAAAAO40%2FicWR3V-nS00%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6228.JPG&h=0df700d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個敗家仔都問過我，點解唔入A7 解放個一百支135老鏡??? （跌到8k好似係） <br />\n<br />\n突然間想回顧下，我呢兩年半學玩攝影之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來，我一直迷失係片幅既迷思之中⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NjiAK5fY8-M/UVj4sW1iYTI/AAAAAAAAO50/klZzozPQ2qw/s1600/IMGP6248.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-NjiAK5fY8-M%2FUVj4sW1iYTI%2FAAAAAAAAO50%2FklZzozPQ2qw%2Fs1600%2FIMGP6248.JPG&h=381d80b8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全片幅係有優勢 但唔等於適合用全部老鏡 特別係Sony Mirrorless 系列. <br />\n<br />\n唔講太多以免阻礙樓主發文 留名以觀其文 A7用家"},{"pid":"ee2862555fdf5fd102052a2f9612ba2c96a6cc4d","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"補貼幾張EOSM轉接： <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ERGIky4gmCU/UlocRf5J_9I/AAAAAAAARMI/cDOxMJl31uI/s1600/IMG_0360.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ERGIky4gmCU%2FUlocRf5J_9I%2FAAAAAAAARMI%2FcDOxMJl31uI%2Fs1600%2FIMG_0360.JPG&h=c35ab2fc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-gLVozlOClzo/UloccWUXW7I/AAAAAAAARLA/bKXFyQ7bV-Q/s1600/IMG_0391.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-gLVozlOClzo%2FUloccWUXW7I%2FAAAAAAAARLA%2FbKXFyQ7bV-Q%2Fs1600%2FIMG_0391.JPG&h=73d75228&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-NXzsUiNoti0/UlocdM6fOFI/AAAAAAAARK4/Gdcl-cbA1S0/s1600/IMG_0395.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-NXzsUiNoti0%2FUlocdM6fOFI%2FAAAAAAAARK4%2FGdcl-cbA1S0%2Fs1600%2FIMG_0395.JPG&h=50ab95f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdea0ff5d8a67653dea3d9e6348582d4ba290510","tid":86331,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全片幅係有優勢 但唔等於適合用全部老鏡 特別係Sony Mirrorless 系列. <br />\n<br />\n唔講太多以免阻礙樓主發文 留名以觀其文 A7用家</bl